Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.57,DefaultBG,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1365,512)\fr17\3c&H48F186&\c&H000000&}\h                                        \h\N我很期待今天看到你的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,男性會把愛慕寫成和歌送給女性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,芹澤同學 你太明目張膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然後這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為美櫻來美術教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,打電話也沒接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,合田同學跑去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是把畫忘在家裡了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,現在可能正急忙跑回家拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽辦 春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要在這裡再等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 等了好久美櫻都沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那天最後還是解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,至於選擇哪幅畫則改天再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻有來學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是她說「今天午餐妳們兩個吃吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她說是有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺美櫻很沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是在煩惱戀愛的畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事...那她幹嘛不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我們今天社團時間問問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會找時間過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,合田同學怎麽樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她今天也沒去社團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,合田同學到底是怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拍攝畫不會花多少時問 是還可以再拖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但最後的場景可沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,先編輯拍好的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大致上都連接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,接著只要導演細部編輯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...我很期待妳的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽說呢 這是電影社最後一部電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是集大成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話 我希望美櫻也能參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麽啊 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請您不要...告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不過啊 合田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 千秋他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝的哥哥本來身體就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他是即使如此當遇到需要幫助的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也會奮不顧身去救人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,千秋那一天也依然...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 合田妳不用感到愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要連他的份也一起好好活下去就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是因為我害春輝同學重要的人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己該用什麽表情面對他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}放學要不要去哪逛逛?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好久沒有三個人一起吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是從暑假以來第一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是在煩惱戀愛的畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妳有跟春輝說什麽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他很擔心妳耶 問妳是不是遇上什麽事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這...樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和尊敬的恩人見面了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對喔 過完盂蘭盆節後有見面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是很棒的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 咦...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,已經永遠見不到那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正好在跟美櫻...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,美櫻?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是怎麽了 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說點什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我怎麽知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 你還是別再和我說話了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爲什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之間甚至遠離了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不止10公分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,合田同學還是沒交戀愛的畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,春輝 怎麽辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最後一幕也還沒拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再等下去 進度上來說會很吃緊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,用早坂的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你有跟合田說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你說進度上會很吃緊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我有打算和她說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可是感覺已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,「不行」是...到底發生什麽事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是什麽都沒有 我才不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,用早坂的畫真的可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不就這樣說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,遲遲不決定 對兩位先畫好的很失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 再等一下下也...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那要等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去等到秋天 季節就和其他場景不符了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,畫的事 我去告訴夏樹她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,導演大人在弄編輯好像很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,火藥味好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是顧問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,明明沒做過半點顧問該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我比較重視社員的自主性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那可以請您離開我的視綫範圍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我會無法專心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我應該怎麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,合田的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說了嗎 我重視自主性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不過嘛 千秋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,應該會説「去做你相信的事就好了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是這麽說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個該怎麽辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,秋哥 秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,秋哥你會翻單槓喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,超帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 咲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咲哥也好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,秋哥你怎麽了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有點生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,生病?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,跟感冒一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這種小病很快就會好了 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊 春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還是過來跟哥哥聊電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 這就是拍攝按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拍攝?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,用這個就能拍出電影囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的電影是那個電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哇塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.20,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}泣きそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.20,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,820)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}な
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:15.14,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}今日もまた失敗しちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:15.14,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,468)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}きょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:15.14,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,742)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}しっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.98,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}こんな時あなたなら...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.98,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,704)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}とき
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:26.78,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}ねぇ 考えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:26.78,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,876)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}かんが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.22,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}愛する人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.22,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,818)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}あい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.22,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an5\fs36\pos(1820,982)\fr-90\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}ひと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:40.00,IN_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fn@Noto Sans CJK SC Medium}どこにいますか? 聞こえますか?
